(283, 402, 'Profile:\n\nIndulge in the rich, velvety embrace of \"Cacao Oscuro Revelation,\" our signature Mexican Chocolate Stout that marries the robust character of traditional stout with the spicy warmth and sweetness of authentic Mexican chocolate. This opulent brew is an homage to the time-honored Mexican chocolate-making tradition, providing an adventurous exploration for the palate, steeped in cultural richness and culinary artistry.', 'Profile:\n\nIndulge in the rich, velvety embrace of \"Cacao Oscuro Revelation,\" our signature Mexican Chocolate Stout that marries the robust character of traditional stout with the spicy warmth and sweetness of authentic Mexican chocolate. This opulent brew is an homage to the time-honored Mexican chocolate-making tradition, providing an adventurous exploration for the palate, steeped in cultural richness and culinary artistry.\n\nAppearance:\n\nCacao Oscuro pours a deep, obsidian hue, as dark and enigmatic as a moonless night. A generous, creamy tan head crowns the brew, reminiscent of the frothy top of a freshly whipped hot chocolate, promising a luxurious experience.\n\nAroma:\n\nThe aroma is a symphony of contrast and harmony - dark roasted malts create an alluring foundation, exuding notes of espresso and dark chocolate, while the air is perfumed with the sweet, cinnamon-infused richness distinctive of Mexican chocolate. Subtle whispers of vanilla and almond offer a hint of sweetness, and a faint, spicy chili presence tickles the nose, adding an invigorating twist to the bouquet.\n\nTaste:\n\nOn the first sip, your taste buds are greeted by the bittersweet character of dark cocoa, robust and full-bodied, characteristic of the stout\'s backbone. This richness is swiftly complemented by the unique profile of Mexican chocolate - the sweetness of cinnamon and sugar, the creamy nuances of vanilla, and the nutty undertones of almond. As the flavor profile deepens, the playful heat of chili peppers emerges, offering a gentle warmth that does not overpower but rather balances the chocolate\'s sweetness. The sip culminates in a melody of these flavors, lingering on the palate and inviting another taste.\n\nMouthfeel:\n\nDespite its bold flavor profile, Cacao Oscuro maintains a silky, almost velvety mouthfeel. The moderate carbonation ensures a smooth ride for all the intricate flavors at play, while the subtle heat from the chili peppers provides a pleasant warmth, stimulating the senses and complementing the beer\'s full body.\n\nOverall Experience:\n\nCacao Oscuro Revelation is not just a beer; it\'s a journey through the rich tapestry of Mexican culinary art, transformed into a liquid delicacy. It\'s an ideal companion for the stout aficionado looking to venture into new territories, or the adventurous drinker seeking a brew that tells a story. Perfect to be savored solo, it also pairs splendidly with rich desserts or hearty, spicy meals. Each sip is a celebration of culture, tradition, and the unending quest for flavors that excite and inspire. Salud!', 1, '2023-11-09 19:27:20', '2023-11-09 19:27:20'),
(284, 403, ' Abbey Ale 6.5%\n\nProfile:\n\nEmbark on a divine journey with \"Monastic Harmony,\" our distinguished Abbey Ale, crafted with reverence to ancient brewing traditions. At 6.5%, this medium-bodied elixir balances spiritual contemplation with joyous liberation, offering a transcendent experience wrapped in the cloak of a monk\'s dedication.', 'Appearance:\n\nThis hallowed brew presents itself in a radiant amber-brown robe, adorned with a persistent off-white head that speaks to the fervent prayers of carbonation beneath.\n\nAroma:\n\nGraceful aromas of ripe fruit meet the nostrils, with hints of banana, clove, and a whisper of caramel sweetness, akin to the scent of a secluded abbey orchard in full bloom.\n\nTaste:\n\nMonastic Harmony\'s flavor is a testament to its name, with the gentle sweetness of malted barley in perfect concert with fruity esters and a hint of spice. The 6.5% alcohol content is artfully masked beneath the ale\'s celestial profile, providing warmth without an overt boozy distraction.\n\nMouthfeel:\n\nSilken yet effervescent, this Abbey Ale offers a medium body and lively carbonation, making each sip a revitalizing mantra of flavor and tradition.\n\nOverall Experience:\n\n\"Monastic Harmony\" is more than a beer; it\'s the liquid hymn of centuries-old brewing devotion. Ideal for quiet reflection or spirited conversation, it pairs beautifully with soft cheeses, hearty stews, or a tranquil moment alone. Let this Abbey Ale elevate your spirit with each harmonious sip. Cheers!', 1, '2023-11-09 19:38:36', '2023-11-09 19:38:36'),
(285, 404, 'Cette blanche complète le trio de notre Série Classique St-Mathieu. Brassée avec une levure belge et un soupçon d’orange, notre Witbier libère un agréable parfum d’agrumes. En bouche, on découvre un goût frais et des saveurs délicates d’orange et de muscade. Cette bière de blé plaira assurément aux amateurs de blanches de type belge.', 'Cette blanche complète le trio de notre Série Classique St-Mathieu. Brassée avec une levure belge et un soupçon d’orange, notre Witbier libère un agréable parfum d’agrumes. En bouche, on découvre un goût frais et des saveurs délicates d’orange et de muscade. Cette bière de blé plaira assurément aux amateurs de blanches de type belge.', 1, '2023-11-14 10:31:31', '2023-11-14 10:31:31'),
